WEBVTT

00:00:12.150 --> 00:00:15.150
♫ Like the heather ♫

00:00:15.150 --> 00:00:19.150
♫ on the hillside ♫

00:00:19.150 --> 00:00:22.150
♫ as they drove us ♫

00:00:22.150 --> 00:00:26.150
♫ from the Highlands ♫

00:00:26.150 --> 00:00:30.150
♫ Like the ice flow ♫

00:00:30.150 --> 00:00:33.150
♫ from the Arctic ♫

00:00:33.150 --> 00:00:37.150
♫ where we landed ♫

00:00:37.150 --> 00:00:42.150
♫ in Newfoundland ♫

00:00:42.150 --> 00:00:47.150
♫ There's a color ♫

00:00:47.150 --> 00:00:50.150
♫ to my sorrow ♫

00:00:50.150 --> 00:00:54.150
♫ There's a name for ♫

00:00:54.150 --> 00:00:57.150
♫ all this sadness ♫

00:00:57.150 --> 00:01:01.150
♫ Like the ocean ♫

00:01:01.150 --> 00:01:04.150
♫ in between us ♫

00:01:04.150 --> 00:01:08.150
♫ I am blue ♫

00:01:12.150 --> 00:01:16.150
♫ Blue is a river ♫

00:01:16.150 --> 00:01:20.150
♫ Blue remembered ♫

00:01:20.150 --> 00:01:25.150
♫ Blue water ♫

00:01:25.150 --> 00:01:28.150
♫ running clear ♫

00:01:28.150 --> 00:01:32.150
♫ Blue like a planet ♫

00:01:32.150 --> 00:01:35.150
♫ to a spaceman ♫

00:01:35.150 --> 00:01:39.150
♫ Blue river ♫

00:01:39.150 --> 00:01:43.150
♫ of my tears ♫

00:01:43.150 --> 00:02:16.150
(Fiddle and synthesizer)

00:02:16.150 --> 00:02:19.150
♫ So I came here ♫

00:02:19.150 --> 00:02:23.150
♫ to the city ♫

00:02:23.150 --> 00:02:27.150
♫ where the dream burns ♫

00:02:27.150 --> 00:02:31.150
♫ like a furnace ♫

00:02:31.150 --> 00:02:35.150
♫ And I dazzled ♫

00:02:35.150 --> 00:02:38.150
♫ in these dark streets ♫

00:02:38.150 --> 00:02:43.150
♫ like a diamond ♫

00:02:43.150 --> 00:02:47.150
♫ in a coalface ♫

00:02:47.150 --> 00:02:51.150
♫ Then the cold wind ♫

00:02:51.150 --> 00:02:54.150
♫ from the islands ♫

00:02:54.150 --> 00:02:58.150
♫ blew a storm cloud ♫

00:02:58.150 --> 00:03:03.150
♫ across the new moon ♫

00:03:03.150 --> 00:03:07.150
♫ Like the gun smoke ♫

00:03:07.150 --> 00:03:10.150
♫ above the houses ♫

00:03:10.150 --> 00:03:14.150
♫ in my home ♫

00:03:17.150 --> 00:03:21.150
♫ Blue is a river ♫

00:03:21.150 --> 00:03:26.150
♫ Blue remembered ♫

00:03:26.150 --> 00:03:30.150
♫ Blue water ♫

00:03:30.150 --> 00:03:33.150
♫ running clear ♫

00:03:33.150 --> 00:03:37.150
♫ Blue like a planet ♫

00:03:37.150 --> 00:03:41.150
♫ to a spaceman ♫

00:03:41.150 --> 00:03:46.150
♫ Blue river ♫

00:03:46.150 --> 00:03:49.150
♫ of my tears ♫

00:03:49.150 --> 00:03:54.150
♫ Blue river ♫

00:03:54.150 --> 00:03:57.150
♫ of my tears ♫

00:03:57.150 --> 00:04:58.150
(Fiddle and synthesizer)

00:04:58.150 --> 00:05:05.150
(Applause)
